            "title": "雲知聲超購30倍  上限205元定價",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">雲知聲(09678)公布招股結果，香港公開發售超認購90.66倍，最終發售價205元，上限定價。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"雲知聲官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/Unisound-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"雲知聲官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/Unisound-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">雲知聲官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">一手(20股)中籤率10.01%，認購500股獲穩派一手。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">按回補機制，公開發售股份已增至62.44萬股，佔發售總數40%。國際發售錄得1.7倍認購。集資淨額2.06億元。</p>\n</div>",
